"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-10-la-planning-no-car-olympics-beat-gridlock\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - Los Angeles (LA) 2028 organisers said Saturday they will force spectators to take public transportation to Olympic venues and encourage remote working in a bid to sidestep the gridlocked city's notorious traffic problems.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 95}, {\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 125}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 143}, {\"ngram\": \"a bid\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"the gridlocked city's notorious traffic problems\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Los Angeles Mayor Karen Bass said 2028 chiefs want the LA Olympics to be \\\"The No Car Games\\\" by investing in public transportation and encouraging Angelenos to adopt pandemic-style remote-working for the duration of the event.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.442663733255019e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2028 chiefs\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"the LA Olympics\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"The No Car Games\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"Angelenos\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"the duration\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The 'No Car Games' means that you will have to take public transportation to get to all of the venues,\\\" Bass told a press conference ahead of Sunday's Paris Olympics closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999125241340532, \"rank\": 8.722013455119716e-05, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday's Paris Olympics closing ceremony\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In order to do that we have been building out our transportation system.\\\"\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"our transportation system\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The plan would require borrowing more than 3,000 buses from other parts of the United States, she added.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.992573541824105, \"rank\": 0.007482023039641384, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The plan\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 3,000 buses\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"other parts\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bass was adamant however that Los Angeles's traffic, where rush hour congestion can lead to car journeys of just a few miles taking an hour or more, would not be a problem, citing the history of the 1984 Olympics in the city.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999125241340532, \"rank\": 8.722013455119716e-05, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}, {\"begin\": 870, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.442663733255019e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rush hour congestion\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"car journeys\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"just a few miles\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"an hour\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1984 Olympics\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 1984 Angelenos were terrified that we were going to have terrible, terrible traffic,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Angelenos\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"terrible, terrible traffic\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And we were shocked that we did not.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And in 1984 we did not have any of the technology that we do today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the technology\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added that city officials 40 years ago encouraged employers to stagger shifts or allowed workers to work remotely to great success.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"city officials\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"employers\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"shifts\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"great success\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we can do that again,\\\" Bass said.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999125241340532, \"rank\": 8.722013455119716e-05, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So part of having a no-car Olympics means getting people not to drive, but also using public transportation to get to the games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"So part\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"a no-car Olympics\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We certainly learned from COVID that you have essential workers, people that must come to work.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"essential workers\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if you limit it to that, it's going to be a lot easier because we did go through COVID.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So people will have some reference point in recent history as to how you can do that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"some reference point\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"recent history\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bass said the city would also aim to house Los Angeles's estimated 75,500 homeless population before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999125241340532, \"rank\": 8.722013455119716e-05, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}, {\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.442663733255019e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if Los Angeles would follow Paris's example by moving several thousand homeless people in the build-up to the Olympics to locations outside the city, Bass replied: \\\"We are going to get Angelenos housed.\\\"\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1991, \"end\": 2002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.442663733255019e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2016, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999909305188, \"rank\": 9.069377641476506e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2138, \"end\": 2142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"score\": 0.9999125241340532, \"rank\": 8.722013455119716e-05, \"text\": \"Bass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bass_guitar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several thousand homeless people\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"locations\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"Angelenos\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is what we have been doing and we are going to continue to do that.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will get people housed, we will get them off the street.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"the street\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will get them into temporary housing, we will address the reasons why they were unhoused and get them into permanent housing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"temporary housing\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"the reasons\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"permanent housing\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sunday's closing ceremony in Paris will mark the formal start of the countdown to the Los Angeles Olympics, with the city offering a preview of what to expect in 2028 as the curtain comes down in the French capital.\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2489, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999909305188, \"rank\": 9.069377641476506e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2660, \"end\": 2666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9989044337023931, \"rank\": 0.0010191848396750528, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunday's closing ceremony\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"the formal start\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"the countdown\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"the Los Angeles Olympics\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"a preview\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"the curtain\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think authentically LA is what you will see in tomorrow's closing ceremonies as a first step,\\\" LA28 chairman Casey Wasserman said.\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2789, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"tomorrow's closing ceremonies\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"a first step\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not have an Eiffel Tower, we have got the Hollywood sign.\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2861, \"end\": 2875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got incredible venues.\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"incredible venues\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got incredible geography and we are going to showcase that both physically and in the way we show up, which I think people will get a sense of tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 3069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"incredible geography\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"tomorrow\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags: HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tags\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3088}]}]}"